beer.beer_description:
A light malt backbone really allows the hops in this XPA to shine. Sessionable but with flavour. Lychee and passion fruit meld brilliantly with Gladiator malt, to give a perfectly balanced, complex, yet highly drinkable beer. XPA has become the go to style for craft beer lovers and our version is extra good, even if we do say so ourselves!

Malt: Pilsner, Gladiator

Hops: Citra, Mosaic
